'''极大望远镜'''（Extremely Large Telescope，簡寫ELT）是指[[天文台|天文台]]使用的直径大于20公尺的[[望远镜|望远镜]]<ref>See title of http://www.astro-opticon.org/fp5/skelcase.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.astro-opticon.org/fp5/skelcase.html |date=20210324024351 }} and section 1 of {{cite web |url=http://www.aao.gov.au/instrum/ELT/ELTroadmap040917.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-03-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050518164822/http://www.aao.gov.au/instrum/ELT/ELTroadmap040917.pdf |archivedate=2005-05-18 }}</ref>。当讨论反射望远镜的光波波长时，包括[[紫外线|紫外线]]（UV），[[光|可见光]]和[[红外线|近红外线]]的波长。在众多的规划中的性能中，极大望远镜预计将增加发现其他恒星周围的[[类地行星|类地行星]]的机会。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/science/2006/aug/05/spaceexploration.universe |title=Extremely Large Telescope could reveal secrets of life, the universe and everything |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |first=Alok |last=Jha |date=5 August 2006 |accessdate=2014-09-01 |archive-date=2011-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110509145033/http://www.guardian.co.uk/science/2006/aug/05/spaceexploration.universe |dead-url=no }}</ref>
对于其他波长的望远镜在物理上可以大得很多，例如，无线电波长的[[绿岸望远镜|绿岸望远镜]]的光圈为{{convert|100|m|yd|abbr=off}}。

这些望远镜有一定数量的特点和共同性，特别是都使用{{link-en|分割式的镜片|Segmented mirror}}组合成主镜（类似于现有的[[凯克天文台|凯克望远镜]]），和使用高阶的[[自适应光学|自适应光学]]系统。<ref name=constr>{{Cite journal |url=http://www.tmt.org/news/TMT-Construction%20Proposal-Public.pdf |publisher=TMT Observatory Corporation |page=29 |title=Thirty Meter Telescope Construction Proposal |date=2007-09-12 |accessdate=2009-07-24 |journal= |archive-date=2016-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324230243/http://tmt.org/news/TMT-Construction%20Proposal-Public.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=design_optics>{{Cite book |title=GMT Conceptual Design Report |chapter=Chapter 6: Optics |url=http://www.gmto.org/CoDRpublic |chapterurl=http://www.gmto.org/codrfolder/GMT-ID-01467-Chapter_6_Optics.pdf |pages=6–3 |accessdate=2008-04-02 |publisher=GMT Consortium |archive-date=2011-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525204134/http://www.gmto.org/CoDRpublic |dead-url=no }}</ref>

虽然极大望远镜的设计都很大，但是它们可以有比许多大型的光学[[干涉仪|干涉仪]]的{{link-en|孔径合成|Aperture synthesis}}更加小的孔径。然而，它们可以收集更多的光，并且有其他的优点。

== 极大望远镜 ==
